the black watch has been approved.

855
01:29:02,074 --> 01:29:05,966
I'm reporting for duty, sir.

856
01:29:05,976 --> 01:29:08,234
The latest "gazette"

857
01:29:08,244 --> 01:29:12,204
has news of interest for you gentlemen.

858
01:29:12,214 --> 01:29:16,006
Major King of the black watch

859
01:29:16,016 --> 01:29:18,942
